<!--
  ~ Replacement notification small icon — DIGEST action.
  ~ Material Symbols outlined `inbox` glyph (24dp). Used by
  ~ SmartNotiNotifier.notifySuppressedNotification(decision = DIGEST, …)
  ~ via ReplacementActionIcon.DIGEST.drawableRes.
